hod will become\nstandard in quantum field theory for confined fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jun 2021 18:05:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2021 06:00:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-03"}
