etry,\nTTI), and obtain the explicit ray velocity derivatives for the coupled qP and\nqSV waves and for SH waves.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jun 2021 22:53:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-01"}
